ActNational Aboriginal Economic Development Board Order
PrecisAppointment of JIM BOUCHER of Fort Mackay, Alberta, to be a member of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years; and designation of JIM BOUCHER as Vice-Chairperson of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board.
